snippet.title: "She's Done" Judge Reveals Giving Johnny Depp Access To Amber Heard's Phone Records
snippet.description:
"She's Done" Judge Reveals Giving Johnny Depp Access To Amber Heard's Phone Records 
In this video, an American judge reveals how impactful it will be that Amber Heard is forced to hand over her phone records to the legal team of Johnny Depp, and thus, they can look through stuff that might mean something. Let's see what happens.
